headline: Cisco (CSCO): Evaluating Valuation After Strong Earnings Beat and Upgraded AI-Driven Outlook
summary: Cisco Systems (CSCO) has kicked off its fiscal year with a strong earnings report that topped both revenue and profit forecasts, and also raised its full-year outlook. The upbeat results are largely tied to surging demand for AI-related infrastructure from cloud providers and corporate clients. See our latest analysis for Cisco Systems.
